Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.50,0:00:03.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喲 卡萊多之星的時間到了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.30,0:00:06.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觀看卡萊多之星的時候要注意保持屋內亮度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.00,0:00:08.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要離電視太近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.20,0:00:13.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那麼 那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.70,0:00:15.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家好 我是瑪莉奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.80,0:00:18.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家喜歡媽媽嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.00,0:00:22.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我媽媽在我很小時因事故而去世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.50,0:00:26.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她是位擅長蹦床的卡萊多之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.00,0:00:29.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是非常溫柔的媽媽哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.30,0:00:31.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到現在都很喜歡媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.80,0:00:36.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我長大後我也想成為像媽媽那樣傑出的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.20,0:02:23.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要迷失夢想 繼續追蹤下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.00,0:02:27.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的前面會展開新的卡萊多之星的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.40,0:02:31.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢想……嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.50,0:02:37.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐知道我迷失了夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.80,0:02:41.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因憧憬蕾拉小姐而進入卡萊多舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.20,0:02:42.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成為像蕾拉小姐那樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.60,0:02:45.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多之星曾是我的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.20,0:02:50.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是追著蕾拉小姐的步程繼續努力下去就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.60,0:02:55.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了那個 無論什麼苦難都能克服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.00,0:03:01.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而 現在卻不知道自己想做什麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.00,0:03:03.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有了夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.60,0:03:08.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.10,0:03:09.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看見爸爸了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.60,0:03:12.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.20,0:03:13.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 瑪莉奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.40,0:03:14.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扮的這麼漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.30,0:03:17.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去看媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.00,0:03:36.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 媽媽喜歡的香水百合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.90,0:03:38.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.30,0:03:42.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在諾桑斯力多角的花店買的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.00,0:03:44.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裏的店員真是怠慢 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.40,0:03:47.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直把我當成小孩對待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.90,0:03:51.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次已經說過了我真的是光火極了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.10,0:03:54.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼“工資高低決定服務態度”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.60,0:03:55.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有呢……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.60,0:03:57.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 瑪莉奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.30,0:04:00.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說這麼多媽媽可要頭暈了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.00,0:04:03.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.60,0:04:08.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬納森 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.00,0:04:16.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間真過得快 西西亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.40,0:04:19.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你過世已經6年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.50,0:04:21.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其間發生很多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.00,0:04:24.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小瑪莉奧已經10歲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.00,0:04:32.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 長的不錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.00,0:04:39.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋回轉•跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.70,0:04:54.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎喲哎喲 怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.40,0:04:55.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.50,0:05:01.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德古拉好嚇人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.50,0:05:04.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦 那是演戲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.30,0:05:06.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要 嚇人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.40,0:05:08.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟 下次再來哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.90,0:05:20.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我不再來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.70,0:05:22.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.50,0:05:26.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.10,0:05:29.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萊恩的德古拉雖然逼真 評價高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.50,0:05:33.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子卻好像被嚇唬住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.40,0:05:35.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得來了真是可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.70,0:05:38.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 好吧 這樣的話……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.10,0:05:40.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒人和你搭檔哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.70,0:05:46.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然卡萊多舞臺必須大人小孩都喜歡才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.50,0:05:51.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都喜歡的舞臺……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.10,0:05:58.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊 這是我的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.00,0:06:01.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.60,0:06:03.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.10,0:06:04.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試試看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.50,0:06:11.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先組合出假設的舞臺再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.10,0:06:13.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.50,0:06:15.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天可以練習了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.10,0:06:17.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是為孩子們表演的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.30,0:06:18.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.80,0:06:22.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,僅在雙休日正式公演 白天和夜間舞臺表演的中間一段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.80,0:06:24.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是空的點子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.10,0:06:28.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把卡萊多舞臺的真正樂趣傳達給所有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.00,0:06:31.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經獲得了老闆的允許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.60,0:06:33.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就差演員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.80,0:06:36.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兒童舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.40,0:06:38.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正式公演的間隙段時間演出？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.10,0:06:39.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.00,0:06:40.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然會很累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.30,0:06:43.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要是大家交替著做的話應該沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.80,0:06:45.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.50,0:06:46.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放棄算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.40,0:06:48.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.50,0:06:52.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觀眾上座率在增加 沒什麼問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.50,0:06:57.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望孩子們也能喜愛卡萊多舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.30,0:07:00.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以兒童舞臺是有必要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.90,0:07:05.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前還是先學會令我滿意的技術來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.30,0:07:07.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這個很重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.20,0:07:09.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我覺得兒童舞臺也很重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.10,0:07:12.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我對著幹嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.60,0:07:14.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不放棄兒童舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.70,0:07:20.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 我在動搖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.10,0:07:21.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.00,0:07:24.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不太妙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.80,0:07:26.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.00,0:07:28.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想把精力集中在現在的角色上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.70,0:07:35.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更多地練習技術來創造出適合萊恩的舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.10,0:07:37.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你陪孩子們好好玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.90,0:07:41.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.80,0:07:43.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也對不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.50,0:07:54.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本以為大家會參加的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.80,0:07:57.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算人數不足也可以表演的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.50,0:07:59.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然我會協助你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.80,0:08:01.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.50,0:08:02.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.50,0:08:03.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛吉特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.90,0:08:07.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我偶爾也想在眾多孩子們面前表演一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.80,0:08:10.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話我和空表演空中飛人也行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.00,0:08:12.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 沒有空中飛人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.80,0:08:14.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.30,0:08:16.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就表演陀螺好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.00,0:08:22.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必殺橫拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.90,0:08:28.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個……可以的話唱唱歌什麼的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.80,0:08:33.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,介紹一種大家不知道的拳法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.00,0:08:34.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.30,0:08:43.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是洛吉特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.20,0:08:50.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下個動作 結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.50,0:08:53.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.40,0:08:54.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.50,0:08:57.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不許扮丑角哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.60,0:09:01.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像是從臉上落下來的 或者說……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.60,0:09:02.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.10,0:09:09.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了哦 喬納森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.60,0:09:14.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了 咦！來了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.30,0:09:16.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要來很多哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.60,0:09:23.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬納森都不理她哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.70,0:09:26.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬納森 拋回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.50,0:09:28.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬納森還沒好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.10,0:09:29.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都還沒有發覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.20,0:09:30.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬納森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.30,0:09:36.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蹩腳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.50,0:09:38.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.50,0:09:39.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.60,0:09:41.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.30,0:09:42.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來玩吧 喬納森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.80,0:09:53.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉奧 真厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.40,0:09:54.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,節奏也掌握很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.90,0:09:57.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是一直在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.30,0:10:01.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說空作為搭檔還有不足處呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.50,0:10:07.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有例行會議的日子我也能代演 但是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.80,0:10:11.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就請瑪莉奧代演怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.20,0:10:13.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 不錯哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.00,0:10:18.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對哦 同齡的人上臺表演一定會讓孩子們高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.80,0:10:22.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來表演 我想表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.30,0:10:23.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就這麼決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.40,0:10:26.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空就表演蹦床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.20,0:10:28.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.50,0:10:35.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬納森學的很快哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.60,0:10:39.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不光是會頂球 還會用鼻子套圈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.90,0:10:40.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.80,0:10:44.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是客人來多了或許會緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.80,0:10:46.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.40,0:10:49.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很能適應壓力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.00,0:10:52.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能上臺表演很高興嗎 瑪莉奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.40,0:10:54.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.20,0:10:59.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為喬納森沒我就不行 沒辦法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.50,0:11:01.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.50,0:11:23.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了哦 喬納森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.90,0:11:37.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你耍詐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.00,0:11:41.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.00,0:11:49.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 走著瞧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.50,0:12:01.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 好玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.70,0:12:02.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真高興啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.80,0:12:04.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和空是組合吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.40,0:12:07.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,組合？咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.00,0:12:14.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉奧在蹦床……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.50,0:12:18.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉奧的媽媽以前是蹦床表演者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.50,0:12:21.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子自己也喜歡蹦床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.90,0:12:26.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為很有才能 所以對她期望過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.20,0:12:30.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但母親去世後就不練了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.60,0:12:49.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉奧 精彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.70,0:12:52.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看見瑪莉奧的蹦床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.10,0:12:53.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.50,0:12:55.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是玩玩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.60,0:13:00.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別跟爸爸說哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.10,0:13:04.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放學後再練哦 喬納森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.60,0:13:13.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉奧蹦床了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.50,0:13:16.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 瑪莉奧的演技 率真而漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.90,0:13:19.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,練習一下會有更多進步的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.60,0:13:26.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉奧在模仿頭牌明星的媽媽時自然地掌握了蹦床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.50,0:13:31.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前經常有人說 今後母女都是卡萊多之星吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.50,0:13:36.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但為什麼放棄了呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.50,0:13:40.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能因為想起媽媽的事感到悲傷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.60,0:13:44.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可能變得害怕跳躍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.90,0:13:46.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.70,0:13:52.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時的瑪莉奧非常活躍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.70,0:13:56.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是她說不要讓爸爸知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.60,0:14:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就是說背著喬偷偷練習？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.50,0:14:12.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.20,0:14:14.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼跟爸爸說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.70,0:14:18.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要說 明明說過不要說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.00,0:14:23.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉奧今天跳過蹦床了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.60,0:14:26.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉奧 爸爸想……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.60,0:14:29.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 我沒跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.70,0:14:32.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬他……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.10,0:14:35.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽見我們的談話了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.70,0:14:38.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.00,0:14:41.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再看見那樣的爸爸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.60,0:14:54.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想再看見那樣悲傷的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.10,0:15:02.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要是跳蹦床受傷的話爸爸會十分悲傷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.30,0:15:08.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我決定不再跳蹦床了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.50,0:15:10.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.10,0:15:14.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 沒能瞭解你的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.00,0:15:18.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.30,0:15:22.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我表演 我想表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.30,0:15:25.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 真的可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.00,0:15:28.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實瑪莉奧是想像媽媽那樣……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.00,0:15:29.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.90,0:15:31.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.70,0:15:34.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.30,0:15:36.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該準備上場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.40,0:15:59.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實瑪莉奧喜歡跳蹦床的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.00,0:16:02.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道就沒有什麼我能為她做的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.50,0:16:17.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射手座正陷入深深的迷惑之黑暗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.80,0:16:19.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擺脫黑暗的關鍵是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.80,0:16:22.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水瓶座少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.30,0:16:38.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉奧 白天的那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.90,0:16:42.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蹦床的事的話 不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.70,0:16:45.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就沒有跳的打算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.20,0:16:50.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉奧 還記得媽媽的舞臺的事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.90,0:16:58.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是漂亮 簡直像自由飛翔於空中的鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.40,0:17:06.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸很喜歡跳著蹦床的媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.00,0:17:07.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.50,0:17:09.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有樣東西想給你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.00,0:17:24.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.10,0:17:27.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.80,0:17:35.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.20,0:17:36.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.60,0:17:39.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽的舞臺筆記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.60,0:17:45.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想到瑪莉奧會悲傷所以隱藏了 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.00,0:17:47.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.00,0:17:53.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是媽媽為了記錄想到的主意而使用的筆記本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.20,0:17:57.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且為了能掌握而練習了無數回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.10,0:18:03.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉奧初次登臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.90,0:18:05.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.70,0:18:07.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽提出演出的點子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.80,0:18:10.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸提出舞臺的主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.90,0:18:17.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也會吵架 每天商量著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.30,0:18:22.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,某一天能和瑪莉奧一起踏上蹦床的舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.10,0:18:24.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是媽媽的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.50,0:18:31.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 我想和媽媽一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.10,0:18:38.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和媽媽一起站在蹦床的舞臺上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.00,0:18:44.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.60,0:18:52.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天聽說你跳了 我很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.30,0:18:56.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想媽媽一定也是這麼想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.30,0:18:58.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.10,0:19:04.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉奧喜歡蹦床的 對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.20,0:19:04.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.90,0:19:08.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就更喜歡它吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.20,0:19:11.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.50,0:19:15.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒 這個不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.20,0:19:16.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很讓人期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.70,0:19:19.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正符合兒童舞臺的印象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.50,0:19:22.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想表演這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.00,0:19:25.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.50,0:19:29.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 瑪莉奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.20,0:19:31.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 西西亞的角色怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.40,0:19:33.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.30,0:19:36.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空 你來做好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.40,0:19:37.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.50,0:19:38.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.70,0:19:42.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說我可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.20,0:19:44.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.60,0:19:49.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就接受了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.10,0:19:51.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.10,0:19:52.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,熱血沸騰了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.90,0:19:56.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說我跟喬納森是一組嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.10,0:19:57.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.80,0:20:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多關照啊 喬納森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.00,0:20:21.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,落下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.20,0:20:27.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬納森給大家來一個 1 2……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.40,0:20:34.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很適合你哦 瑪莉奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.00,0:20:52.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是媽媽呆過的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.50,0:20:57.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 跳！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.80,0:21:33.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jump
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.50,0:21:36.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.00,0:21:40.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟空一起表演 大家都會有笑臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.90,0:21:42.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.90,0:21:50.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不惜違背我做出來的東西就是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.70,0:21:56.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.00,0:21:57.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 萊恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.90,0:22:15.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在笑 這是真正的卡萊多舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.60,0:22:25.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也許就是我想要的卡萊多舞臺！舞臺！舞臺！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.80,0:23:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集預告\N卡萊多之星 新生之翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.00,0:23:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是被稱為死神的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.40,0:23:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.10,0:23:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年一度的雜技大賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.70,0:23:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上一屆 優勝者是黃金不死鳥的演員蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.70,0:23:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭檔是死神萊恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.50,0:23:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有襲擊梅的悲劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.40,0:24:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要堅持到底！到底！到底！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.80,0:24:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集卡萊多之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.20,0:24:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀是夢想 飛向空
